title: Week 10 NFL Preview & QB Talk with Jordan Palmer
itunes:title: Week 10 NFL Preview & QB Talk with Jordan Palmer
description:
DJ & Bucky open the show discussing Dez Bryant to the Saints (1:20), then the guys preview all the matchups on the Week 10 NFL slate (5:12). Former NFL QB and current QB trainer/coach Jordan Palmer joins the show to discuss the rookie QB class & what he has seen this fall from some of the top college QB in the nation & how they translate to the pro game (24:30). DJ & Bucky end the show with their college picks for Week 11: including 4 top-25 matchups: 2 Clemson at 17 BC, 16 Miss St at 1 Alabama, 24 Auburn at 5 Georgia, 10 Ohio St at 18 Michigan St (45:50).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
